---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About"
  description="The Mole Clinic is a UK specialist dermatology business. We built this CPD because physios see skin every day."
>
  <section class="bg-tmc-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-3">About this programme</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 prose prose-slate">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-tmc-primary mb-4">About The Mole Clinic</h2>
      <p class="text-tmc-text leading-relaxed mb-5">
        The Mole Clinic is the UK's leading skin cancer check and mole removal clinic. We provide
        award-winning skin checks, mole checks and advanced mole mapping, delivered by expert
        clinicians using the latest diagnostic technology. Rated 'Excellent' by patients and
        approved by all major UK insurers, we offer fast, reliable assessments for early detection
        and peace of mind.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-tmc-primary mb-4 mt-8">Why we built this CPD</h2>
      <p class="text-tmc-text leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Physiotherapists see skin every session. Whether you're treating a runner's calf, a
        golfer's forearm, or a swimmer's back, you have an unparalleled view of areas your
        patients rarely check themselves — and that most GPs won't see until there's already a
        problem.
      </p>
      <p class="text-tmc-text leading-relaxed mb-5">
        This programme gives you the knowledge to act on what you see: to recognise the signs,
        start the conversation, and connect patients with the right specialist at the right time.
        It's free, it takes under an hour, and it could save a life.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-tmc-text/60 mt-8">
        Learn more about our clinics at{' '}
        <a
          href="https://themoleclinic.co.uk"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-tmc-accent hover:text-tmc-primary underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors"
        >
          themoleclinic.co.uk
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
